---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Herramientas | Omar Fuentes"
  description="Herramientas y utilidades gratuitas para SEO, marketing y creación de contenido."
>
  <main class="pt-24 pb-20 bg-white">
    <div class="px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-12 mx-auto max-w-5xl">
      <header class="mb-10">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-4">Herramientas</h1>
        <p class="text-black text-lg max-w-3xl">
          Utilidades rápidas para ayudarte a crear contenido y mejorar tu SEO.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <a
          href="/herramientas/generador-estructura-articulos/"
          class="group block rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white shadow-sm p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-all"
        >
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-blue via-primary-yellow to-primary-green text-white px-4 py-3 mb-4">
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold opacity-90">Herramienta</div>
            <div class="text-xl font-black">Generador de estructura de artículos</div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary-blue/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 6h8M8 10h8M8 14h6M7 3h10a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-700">
              Crea un esquema completo (H2/H3, FAQ, tablas y más) a partir de una palabra clave.
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-primary-blue text-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold group-hover:bg-accent-blue transition-colors">
              Abrir herramienta
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
              </svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a
          href="/herramientas/generador-titulos-seo/"
          class="group block rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white shadow-sm p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-all"
        >
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-blue via-primary-yellow to-primary-green text-white px-4 py-3 mb-4">
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold opacity-90">Herramienta</div>
            <div class="text-xl font-black">Generador de títulos SEO</div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary-green/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 7h10M7 11h10M7 15h6M12 19l-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h12a2 2 0 012 2v6l-4 4-2 2-2 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-700">
              Genera 10 títulos en segundos: elige un tono, ingresa keyword + tema y exporta.
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-primary-green text-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold group-hover:bg-accent-green transition-colors">
              Abrir herramienta
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
              </svg>
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
